Package: correlation
Title: Simple Tools for Exploring Linear Relationships
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Hasti", "Jalali", , "hastii.jalali@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a lightweight function for fitting a simple linear 
    regression between two numeric variables and returning the slope, 
    intercept, and R-squared value in a tidy tibble. Useful for quick 
    exploratory analysis and teaching basic regression concepts.
